src:
Kolstad-spilleren briljerte i rekordkampen - feide serielederen av banen
02 Nov 2019, 18:50 by Even Berthelsen
Det som var ventet som en tett og jevn affære ble isteden en ren fest for Kolstad. Det kan de takke keeperen sin for.

Kolstad – Drammen 31 – 21 (17 – 10)
text:
The Kolstad player shone in the record game - swept the series leader of the field
02 Nov 2019, 18:50 by Even Berthelsen
What was expected as a close and steady affair instead became a pure celebration for Kolstad. They can thank their keeper for that.

Kolstad - Drammen 31 - 21 (17 - 10)
